FBIS4-39742 "drsov112_b_94005" FBIS-SOV-94-112 Daily Report 10 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Signs Edict on Social Accord Treaty Yeltsin Signs Edict on Social Accord Treaty LD1006083994 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 0700 GMT 10 Jun 94 LD1006083994 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Russian BFN [Text] President Boris Yeltsin has signed an edict on measures to implement the treaty on public accord. A conciliation commission [soglasitelnaya komissiya] is being set up to deal with this. Sergey Filatov, the head of the president's administration, has been appointed its chairman. The conciliation commission will cooperate in its work with the Federal Assembly's Federation Council and State Duma, as well as with parties, social and public movements, and other organizations whose representatives signed the treaty on public accord.
